### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [FAIL] Sales user mencoba membuat produk baru (tidak berwenang)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_sales}}

{
  "name": "Gagal Product",
  "price": 99.99
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Admin membuat produk baru
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}

{
  "name": "Layanan Konsultasi Premium",
  "description": "Sesi konsultasi strategis selama 1 jam.",
  "price": 1500.00
}


### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Mendapatkan semua produk (bisa diakses oleh semua peran terotentikasi)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token_viewer}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Mendapatkan produk berdasarkan ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_sales}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [FAIL] Mendapatkan produk dengan ID tidak valid
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{token_sales}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Admin memperbarui produk
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}

{
  "price": 1750.00,
  "description": "Sesi konsultasi strategis eksklusif selama 1 jam."
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [FAIL] Sales user mencoba memperbarui produk (tidak berwenang)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token_sales}}

{
  "price": 1800.00
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Admin menonaktifkan produk (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [VERIFY] Cek bahwa produk yang dinonaktifkan sudah tidak ada di daftar
GET {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token_sales}}

### ----------------------------------------------------------------

### [FAIL] Mencoba menghapus produk yang sudah dihapus (akan error 'not found')
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}

